div.p:
The total expenses of the state in 1874, in France, amount to 1,091,700,000
                    florins; in Russia, to 956,200,000 florins; in Germany, to 864,300,000 florins;
                    in Austria-Hungary, 635,131,000 florins.

list.item:
Thirdly. Navy.—Claimed, 8,643,254 florins;
allowed, 8,048,410 florins. Allowance of previous year, 8,642,290
florins.

Thirdly. Navy.—Claimed, 1,327,780 florins;
allowed, 1,287,780 florins. Allowance previous year, 1,296,984
florins.
